<h1><a name="Ini_Configuration"></a>  <strong>Ini Configuration</strong> </h1>
<p />
<div class="twikiToc"> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#About_this_Document"> About this Document</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#General_Layout"> General Layout</a>
